{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Cr2PNAy53EwzHYirnL6Xxh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. Let me analyze and plan the migration:\n\n**Current State:**\n- Jakarta EE 10 app with Open Liberty runtime\n- JSF (Jakarta Faces) web UI with EJB session beans\n- JPA entities with H2 in-memory database\n- WAR packaging\n\n**Migration Strategy:**\n- Convert JSF + EJB to Quarkus REST (JAX-RS) endpoints + CDI beans\n- Keep JPA entities (Quarkus supports `jakarta.persistence` annotations)\n- Replace EJB @Stateful/@Singleton with CDI @ApplicationScoped/@RequestScoped\n- Replace JSF UI with REST API endpoints\n- Use Quarkus Hibernate ORM with H2\n- Use `quarkus-maven-plugin` for build"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29643,"cache_read_input_tokens":19651,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":29643,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":597},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"55e73a7c-4fe4-4151-9924-02c4bb9835cf","uuid":"e51a0658-b629-476e-8b4f-f2cbd2360977"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Cr2PNAy53EwzHYirnL6Xxh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01JmJVWQsPQBHtXAEwD2mrCU","name":"TodoWrite","input":{"todos":[{"content":"Analyze existing codebase structure","status":"completed","activeForm":"Analyzing existing codebase structure"},{"content":"Create new Quarkus pom.xml with proper dependencies","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Creating new Quarkus pom.xml"},{"content":"Create application.properties for Quarkus","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating application.properties"},{"content":"Refactor entities for Quarkus/Hibernate compatibility","status":"pending","activeForm":"Refactoring entities"},{"content":"Convert EJB RequestBean to CDI service bean","status":"pending","activeForm":"Converting RequestBean to CDI"},{"content":"Convert EJB ConfigBean to CDI startup bean","status":"pending","activeForm":"Converting ConfigBean to CDI"},{"content":"Create REST endpoints to replace JSF UI","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating REST endpoints"},{"content":"Generate smoke tests","status":"pending","activeForm":"Generating smoke tests"},{"content":"Update Dockerfile for Quarkus","status":"pending","activeForm":"Updating Dockerfile"},{"content":"Build Docker image and run tests","status":"pending","activeForm":"Building and testing Docker image"},{"content":"Document all actions in CHANGELOG.md","status":"pending","activeForm":"Documenting in CHANGELOG.md"}]}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29643,"cache_read_input_tokens":19651,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":29643,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":597},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"55e73a7c-4fe4-4151-9924-02c4bb9835cf","uuid":"b4cb1126-88c8-4612-8ec8-81266f28e473"}
